title: U.S. Dollar Dives After Powell's Dovish Comments: Analysis For EUR/USD, GBP/USD, USD/CAD, USD/JPY
text: Powell signaled that Fed was ready to cut rates in September.

title: EUR/USD jumps above 1.1700 on Powell's dovish words
text: The US Dollar (USD) collapsed as Federal Reserve (Fed) Chair Jerome Powell delivered his speech at a Jackson Hole Symposium, with EUR/USD peaking at 1.1707, up roughly 100 pips in the last few minutes on Friday.
